## Premium Website Guarantee

**This system ensures uniqueness through:**

1. **Forced choice**: Brand personality MUST be selected
2. **Anti-slop**: Blocks Inter, blue-500, purple gradients
3. **Curated fonts**: 12 distinctive pairings (NOT Inter)
4. **Curated colors**: 10 premium palettes (NOT SaaS blue)
5. **Motion matching**: Animation → brand personality
6. **Polish pass**: Final quality gate

**Result**: Every website built through this system will feel unique and premium - NOT generic AI output.